    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use, but no major dents or rust. Inside, the cabin is tidy and well-preserved, though there is slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it starts right up and drives smoothly, with all major systems functioning as expected. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car that has been cared for properly.",
