    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I've treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always parked in the shade and hand-washed every weekend. It\u2019s in absolutely gorgeous shape, inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, crisp feeling you only get with a car that\u2019s been truly pampered. There might be a tiny, almost invisible speck here or there from life on the road, but you'd have to look real hard to find 'em! Come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of it.",
