      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in automotive engineering. This specimen boasts factory-spec tolerances with a powertrain that exhibits zero parasitic loss. The longitudinal stability is unparalleled thanks to a meticulously dialed-in suspension geometry and fresh bushings throughout. Every fluid change has been performed at sub-interval schedules, ensuring internal combustion harmonics remain crisp and gear synchronization is instantaneous. This isn't just a driver\u2019s car; it\u2019s a preserved artifact of mechanical purity, featuring a throttle response that is nothing short of surgical. The chassis remains stiff, the power delivery is perfectly linear across the entire torque curve, and the aesthetic condition is indistinguishable from the showroom floor.",
